item.title: You Won't Believe How Old Rapper Dream Is Now!
item.description: Introduction Dream is one of the most successful rappers of the 21st century. From his breakthrough single Throw It Back to his successful debut album It’s About Time, Dream has made a name for himself in the rap game. But what many people don’t know is that Dream is actually much older than what you would expect. Read on to learn more about Dream’s career and current life. Overview of Dream’s Career Dream began his career in the early 2000s with his breakout single Throw It Back.
